  Agent guidance:
  When starting a Spring context, set test properties to avoid external telemetry export attempts, e.g. otel.traces.exporter=none, otel.metrics.exporter=none, and otel.logs.exporter=none. Prefer a small ApplicationContextRunner or non-network SpringApplication setup and close the context after assertions.
  
